BitCoin Extension for Bugzilla
------------------------------


DISCLAIMER: This could eat all of your bugs, bitcoins, trash your wallet, etc, 
You take full responsibility for this when using this product.

Assigns Every bug a BitCoin Address / Shows Coins Donated for each bug


MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS
--------------------

Bugzilla: 3.6.1 
Bitcoin: 3.3 
Perl Modules: JSON::RPC::Client 
(apt-get install libjson-rpc-perl)





INSTALL
-------

BACKUP Your bugzilla database, .bitcoin folder before starting!

1. Install BitCoin(d) in Server Mode on a machine the bugzilla installation has access to, set a password for it

2. Place folder in your bugzilla 3.6.1+ extensions dir

3. Login as Administrator to Bugzilla -> Administration -> BitCoin Extension -> Configure as Required

6. Validate Communication - http://server/bugzilla/page.cgi?id=bitcoin.html

5. Run Sanity Check

6. Profit!

